ReturnPolicy.Description:
If you have any problems, please choose "I have a question about using my item or I want to send the seller a message" found on the contact seller and find answers page. I strive to give great customer service, and I will respond ASAP.

Please notify me via eBay messaging within 3 days of delivery if you intend to return this item. I will issue a full refund minus your return shipping cost as long as I receive it in the same condition and within 30 days from the date it was delivered to you. When you mail the item back, please be sure to insure & track the package to protect both of us in case of loss or damage in the mail and please also email me the return tracking number. 

If item is received damaged, please keep original box & packaging and email me pics via eBay messaging of the box showing the shipping label and the damage to the box & the item. USPS requires pictures of the box and the damaged item when filing a claim and for you to hold onto the box and item for 20 days once the case is filed, in case they need to inspect it. 

Thank you and Blessings from Texas!!!
